<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="41" type="type locality">
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="41">Type locality.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="2" pageNumber="41">
Paredones stream, on the outskirts of Paredones village, Dolores Hidalgo, Guanajuato, Mexico (
<geoCoordinate degrees="21" direction="north" minutes="11" orientation="latitude" precision="1" seconds="20.60" value="21.189054">21°11'20.60&quot;N</geoCoordinate>
; 
<geoCoordinate degrees="101" direction="west" minutes="06" orientation="longitude" precision="1" seconds="53.40" value="-101.11483">101°06'53.40&quot;W</geoCoordinate>
; 2089 m a.s.l). Collected by Demetrio Mora on 07.09.2014.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="2" pageNumber="41" type="registration">
